main event: A civilian reported seeing a reddish-like round object floating slowly in Rockaway, Oregon on December 7, 1955.
interesting points: The object was observed creeping along at a height of approximately 75 to 100 feet above the ground., The observation lasted for about 5 minutes., The object did not disappear during the sighting., The course of the object was approximately 350-4 north., There were no photographs or physical evidence documented.
